com.google.api.client.googleapis.notifications

Class TypedNotification<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.google.api.client.googleapis.notifications.AbstractNotification
      • com.google.api.client.googleapis.notifications.TypedNotification<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - Java type of the notification content

    @Beta
public class TypedNotification<T>
extends AbstractNotification
    Beta
    Notification metadata and parsed content sent to this client about a watched resource.

    Implementation is not thread-safe.

    Since:
    1.16
    Author:
    Yaniv Inbar, Matthias Linder (mlinder)
